name: The Camp
Lore: 'An isolated camp protected by Obi-Wan and Captain Panaka was established at the Queen''s starship while Qui-Gon searched for a way to repair the leaking hyperdrive.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Each non-battleground docking bay generates no more than one Force for either player. Opponent''s aliens deploy +1 on Tatooine (or +2 if non-unique or to same Tatooine site as your Jedi, or +4 if both). (Immune to Alter.)',
